export const VocabWords = [
    {
        "kanji": "N/A",
        "characters": "はい",
        "romaji": "hai",
        "part": "interjection",
        "meaning": ["yes"]
    },
    {
        "kanji": "山",
        "characters": "やま",
        "romaji": "yama",
        "part": "noun / counter",
        "meaning": ["mountain; hill", "heap; pile"]
    },
    {
        "kanji": "今日は",
        "characters": "こんにちは",
        "romaji": "konnichiwa",
        "part": "interjection",
        "meaning": ["hello; good day; good afternoon - used during daytime"]
    },
    {
        "kanji": "卵/玉子",
        "characters": "たまご",
        "romaji": "tamago",
        "part": "noun",
        "meaning": ["eggs; egg; spawn; roe"]
    },
    {
        "kanji": "一",
        "characters": "いち",
        "romaji": "ichi",
        "part": "numeric / prefix",
        "meaning": ["one", "best", "first; foremost", "beginning; start"]
    },
    {
        "kanji": "N/A",
        "characters": "を",
        "romaji": "wo",
        "part": "particle",
        "meaning": ["indicates direct object of action",
        "indicates subject of causative expression",
        "indicates an area traversed",
        "indicates time (period) over which action takes place",
        "indicates point of departure or separation of action",
        "indicates object of desire, like, hate, etc."]
    }
]
